      "text": "グループは誕生日が近い人達で組ませてもらったが……\n日頃の疲れを存分に癒して来てくれ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I grouped people whose birthdays are close together…\nSo‚ please relax and recover from your daily fatigue!",
